            "answer_text": "It depends on context and how you\u2019re using \u201cquickly said.\u201d If you mean something like \u201c\u2018No, I will not go out with you,\u2019 she quickly said,\u201d then you could substitute suggestions others here have already made. But if you mean it in the sense of a substitute for, or summarizing, some long explanation or statement, as in \u201cThe explanation of this is [blah blah blah blah] or, quickly said, _____,\u201d then you could substitute an expression such as \u201cin short,\u201d \u201cin summary,\u201d or \u201cbriefly stated.\u201d ",
